Voting Rules

The rules under which votes can be palced for the role of Chairperson to the Board of NFT Bank are:

•	One vote per shareholder
•	Shareholders must register to receive a One Time Password (OTP)
•	The OTP identifies the shareholder in the blockchain allowing them to cast a single secure and unique vote to the shareholder’s preferred candidate
•	While casting their vote the system will also record an image of the shareholder placing the vote to eradicate manipulation of the system
•	All votes are required to be entered within the ‘Election Duration’ to be deemed as valid.
